,\"open_new_tab\":false}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,49,'2025-12-29 14:40:51','2025-12-29 14:41:32','2026-04-02 01:33:53'),(27,'Prospectus','prospectus',NULL,' Prospectus (English Version) of DCGPSC',NULL,'[{\"text\":\" Prospectus (English Version) of DCGPSC\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/107Na7LIsc5TmAYCeOl1iIAg-EsoZmilp\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":true}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-29 14:56:05','2025-12-29 14:57:05','2026-04-01 23:54:18'),(28,'Class Room','class-room','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gJQpSK96iF7meb4VKTSuHh8d3tH3BiBV/view?usp=sharing','The Institution has 68 well decorated classrooms. The Classrooms Present a learner friendly environment. Besides, there are 52 multimedia classrooms in the institution. Here, teachers can take classes using multimedia projector and digital content.',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,55,'2025-12-29 17:16:36','2025-12-29 17:20:45','2026-03-26 04:19:38'),(29,'Indoor Game','indoor-game',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1FACC3BelDSHaQqLXPItbwA4kv70gHlwT&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,56,'2025-12-29 17:20:44','2025-12-29 17:22:59','2025-12-29 17:27:53'),(30,'Outdoor Games','outdoor-games',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=18dFRXFCUHH5k0ypmCTi2QWWJUm_aPI_j&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,57,'2025-12-29 17:22:59','2025-12-29 17:24:21','2025-12-29 17:28:08'),(31,'Library','library','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1M8fi1O-D0rY2zaPCKeJ0niIrQ2iHgMWR/view?usp=sharing','The Institution has a pally air conditioned modern library with seating arrangement of 100 Students. It is enriched with five thousand books. It is named as “Lt Col Zayed Memorial Library and Information Centre” recognizing his contribution for establishing the library.',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,58,'2025-12-29 17:24:21','2025-12-29 17:25:47','2026-03-26 04:48:36'),(32,'Lab','lab','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WuKx3JwBkJhxItC2IvWmnSnjuYsHxx77/view?usp=sharing','The institution has four laboratories. \nThey are: \n\n\n1.    Physics Lab \n2.    Chemistry Lab \n3.    Biology Lab\n4.    Computer Lab \nAll the labs are newly renovated and are equipped with all necessary instruments and modern amenities. Computer lab is fully air conditioned and is facilitated with internet access students can also avail  \n\nN-Computing system in the Lab. ',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-29 17:25:47','2025-12-29 17:27:19','2026-04-01 11:08:22'),(33,'Language Club','language-club',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1X9KOhq8VAvbQd5pi-F1oeWPJ34UaVT0D&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-29 17:27:19','2025-12-29 17:31:36','2025-12-29 17:54:21'),(34,'Debate Club','debate-club',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1xRRPdVWAmjhGtaqY1RLZbU5x4ypFgJOJ&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-29 17:31:36','2025-12-29 17:54:21','2025-12-29 17:56:05'),(35,'GK and Current Affairs','gk-and-current-affairs',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1PNxRqDCSqRHJ3u7b7HmVpELtIaqiMiDw&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-29 17:54:21','2025-12-29 17:56:05','2025-12-29 18:01:24'),(36,'Quranic Club','quranic-club',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1Yl-BC-_PfdA6amDkspIQfPosIGqaiKbH&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,63,'2025-12-29 17:56:05','2025-12-29 18:01:24','2025-12-29 18:03:19'),(37,'Calligraphy and arts and crafts Society','calligraphy-and-arts-and-crafts-society',NULL,'<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1-XpDK2d61aRZqNg5odOeiT9eV4EG-m5Q&sz=w800\" alt=\"Admission\" class=\"circular-photo\">',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,64,'2025-12-29 18:01:24','2025-12-29 18:02:53','2025-12-29 18:03:33'),(39,'Admission Test - 2026','admission-test-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Notice content will be added here.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-03-16 04:00:56','2026-03-16 04:02:11','2026-03-16 04:02:11'),(40,'Teachers Recruitment Circular - 2026','teachers-recruitment-circular-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Notice content will be added here.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-02-18 04:03:21','2026-03-16 04:04:23','2026-03-16 04:04:23'),(41,'Final Recruitment Result - 2026','final-recruitment-result-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Notice content will be added here.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-02-10 04:04:23','2026-03-16 04:06:00','2026-03-16 04:06:00'),(42,'KG - X Seat Plan has been Published','kg-x-seat-plan-has-been-published-notice',NULL,'<p>Notice content will be added here.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-01-29 04:06:00','2026-03-16 04:11:13','2026-03-16 04:11:13'),(43,'Teachers Recruitment Circular','teachers-recruitment-circular-notice',NULL,'<p>Notice content will be added here.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-01-19 04:11:13','2026-03-16 04:13:06','2026-03-16 04:13:06'),(44,'Mission & Vision','mission-vision',NULL,'[](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1voEn52WRO9HonH22lKyyXUvzUauSdf3H/view?usp=sharing)\n# Mission & Vision of DCGPSC\n\nDhaka Cantt Girls’ Public School & College seeks to produce academically well-educated young women, with highly developed interpersonal skills and a broad range of interests, who can compete at any level with the brightest and the best, both nationally and internationally.\n\nObjectives\n1. 1.To make each girl as an asset to ensure their participation in various social and cultural activities.\n2. 2.To inspire each student to exhibit honesty, discipline, wisdom, competence, humanity and dedication in their character.\n3. 3.To inculcate dynamic leadership qualities in each student through various co-curricular activities\n4. 4.To enable the students to go ahead and introduce them with the modern technology.\n5. 5.To make a conscious citizen inspired by the feelings of humanity, honesty, patriotism and our liberation war.\n6. 6.To make a promised citizen inspired by the feelings of solidarity, diversity and mutual harmony.',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-03-23 09:22:57','2026-03-23 09:23:48','2026-04-01 23:23:29'),(45,'Class I Admission Test Result - 2026','class-i-admission-test-result-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Please have a look on the attached file for the result and admission instructions.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-01-19 08:06:14','2026-03-30 09:25:03','2026-03-30 09:25:03'),(46,'Class One Admission Test – 2026 Seat Plan & Schedule','class-one-admission-test-2026-seat-plan-schedule-notice',NULL,'<p>Class One Admission Test – 2026 Seat Plan &amp; Schedule<br>The seat plan and examination schedule for the Class One Admission Test have been published.<br>Please check carefully and attend the exam on time.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-01-08 09:25:03','2026-03-30 09:26:26','2026-03-30 09:26:26'),(47,'Admission Circular Session - 2026','admission-circular-session-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Please have a look on the notice for details.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-01-07 09:26:26','2026-03-30 09:28:41','2026-03-30 09:28:41'),(48,'Class Schedules -2025','class-schedules-2025-notice',NULL,'<p>Class Schedules -2025</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-30 09:28:41','2026-03-30 09:30:03','2026-03-30 09:30:03'),(49,'Class One (BV) Admission Circular Session - 2026','class-one-bv-admission-circular-session-2026-notice',NULL,'<p>Please have a look on the notice for details.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2025-12-21 09:30:03','2026-03-30 09:31:26','2026-03-30 09:31:26'),(51,'Class Routine','class-routine',NULL,'Class Routine',NULL,'[{\"text\":\"Class Routine-01-03-2022\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1EvbblR1RtPotzXEE2BvdXgtSbEpTPTUN