Business Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1ISZZTGh-deb_vRQh-WRIXhLTArLiatbR\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Exam Routine & Syllabus :: Class Test -2018 (Class: XI _ Science & Business Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1-Co9DmX9WmWj7B7Q-A8loq3V6lLuXRNZ\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Exam Routine :: Pretest -2018 (Class XII - Science & Business Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1UG1dfgquWw10_ZPAi508stk7zqxbDqYr\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Exam Routine :: 3rd Monthly Test -2018 for Class XII (Science & Business Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"HSC Final Model Test -2018\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"2nd Monthly Test -2018 (Class XI)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Routine of Quiz Test Examination-2017 for class-XI\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Routine of Pretest Examination-2017 for class-XII\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"5th Monthly Test -2017_Class: XII (Science & B.Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.dcgpsc.edu.bd\\/\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Exam Routine: 4th Monthly Test -2017_Class: XI (Science & B.Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1m2wQJruGHnCDiHWI1A_4mtFVmAAUmIcR\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Exam Routine: HSC Final Model Test - 2017\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1t1pu9SVKekspbBEtrtJeaO3uSsf7kR4-\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"3rd Monthly Exam Routine -2017 - XI (Science-B.Studies)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1E46jAC6Fo4SYMmCqTU7kHe_LhG59UpiG\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"HSC Test Exam Routine-2015\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1gh_TeT1oByqLIp_cEqQKe2l-EH1OUmfq\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Final Exam Routine-2015 (School)\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1obqy1QSBdGHBLSssC-HYgYB14VT-sLjb\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2026-04-01 10:29:16','2026-04-01 10:39:30','2026-04-01 11:02:24'),(53,'Academic Calander','academic-calander',NULL,'Academic Calander',NULL,'[{\"text\":\"Academic Calendar - 2024\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/11RocslM-nfx68QoYdveOtu69SuQBxqEk\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Academic Calendar of 2021\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/18bN-QQpVY7plZAyN-qA-auRUM2EgynJE\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Academic Calendar 2019\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1rHn7S2p4RePIkEPNafgF7VjvEiep3ixw\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"Academic Calendar 2019\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1NjZELGNZ0aBUanaOxxTs_IWi9GCFAocV\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,73,'2026-04-01 10:57:34','2026-04-01 11:01:52','2026-04-01 11:02:56'),(54,'Transport of DCGPSC','transport-of-dcgpsc','https://drive.google.com/file/d/18mswV50XvZZFHRRyTNkPPFyOovX9YTPE/view?usp=sharing','There are five buses for transportation of the students of this institution with the capacity of carrying about 201 students. \n\nThere are also a microbus and a private car for official use.\n\nRespected guardians are requested to contact 01769051740 to avail transport services. ',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,74,'2026-04-01 11:04:44','2026-04-01 11:05:30','2026-04-01 11:11:11'),(55,'Auditorium of DCGPSC','auditorium-of-dcgpsc','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1_SzjtUS4rukJCfnBa_ebLhyydrAIm7lP/view?usp=sharing','We have air-conditioned well decorated auditorium with accommodation of 600 Students. We celebrate the national festivals, arrange various types of debate, quiz, cultural programs and competitions there. We also arrange seminars inviting famous personalities of country throughout the year.',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,75,'2026-04-01 11:05:30','2026-04-01 11:06:36','2026-04-01 11:12:16'),(56,'Playground of DCGPSC','playground-of-dcgpsc','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1CWO2ZIdMUTCwyfkwHK063FiD_7YpwA8o/view?usp=sharing','There is a large playground in this institution. Students play cricket football and other games in the playground. There is also a basketball ground beside the main playground. The Annual Sports of this institution is held in the playground every year. \n',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,76,'2026-04-01 11:06:36','2026-04-01 11:08:22','2026-04-01 11:13:02'),(57,'Infrastructure ','infrastructure','https://drive.google.com/file/d/1v5_vkuF26JfLpQm8eHa17lOZsrDGeIuU/view?usp=sharing','DCGPSC has 3 academic buildings, a modern air conditioned auditorium, a multipurpose hall room, a language centre, an enriched library, Science Labs, and 5 multimedia class room and a canteen.\n\nA Modern Library \nThe institution has a rich modern library with five thousand books. The library is fully air conditioned where there is an excellent seating arrangement of 100 students. It is named Lt Col Zayed Memorial Library and Information Centre” recognizing his contribution as principal of his tenure. \n\nComputer Lab  \nThere are three modern Computer Lab with 62 computers. The lab is facilitated with Internet access. The lab is fully air conditioned where there is an excellent seating arrangement of 120 students at a time. Students avail N Computing system in the Lab.\n\nInformation Centre \nThere is a information centre where all personal information of each students are stored in a computer. This centre is responsible to send information regarding absentee students, various notices and results of various exams through SMS to guardians/teachers.\n\nMini Language Lab \nThe institute has a mini Language Lab which is fully air conditioned. The Lab works for the development of the skills of English Language among the students.\n\nCommon Room \nThere is a common room with good facilities. The students pass their leisure hours playing different kinds of indoor games. \n\nBasket Ball Ground and Play Ground \nThere are a basketball ground and two playgrounds in the institution. The institution has a Children’s Park ‘Annondolok’ where students of Nursery to KG pass their leisure hours and enjoy different games for their physical and mental development.\n\nMultipurpose Hall \nThere is a modern air conditioned Multipurpose Hall which is used for conducting movie classes of different sections of the same class. Meetings and different programs are held there. \n\nMultimedia Classrooms \nThe institution has 52 Multimedia Projectors which are used for taking classes, showing educative movies, conducting different programs and the presentation of results of the exams.\n\nModern Auditorium \nThere is an air conditioned Auditorium with the capacity of accumulating 600 students where major programs are held throughout the year.\n\nCanteen \nThe institution has a Canteen for students and teachers. Snacks and different stationeries are available there. A Canteen Committee controls the price of items and regularly monitors the cleanliness and standard of foods.',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,77,'2026-04-01 23:21:56','2026-04-01 23:23:29','2026-04-01 23:23:55'),(58,'Public Exam Result','public-exam-result',NULL,'Public Exam Result',NULL,'[{\"text\":\"SSC Result 2022\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1jCf0AUkHw7e3UVskSpbKQxN7zGZaqAep\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"HSC Result of 2019\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/183Bk3ahQZdKeapiicmvEFPADBdeaKlah\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"SSC Result of 2019\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1ZU1ZsPnA-JeOlnFmDSZeR4tcjNQN_xR7\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"JSC Result of 2018\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1KYyiF9XctoUb9D9pHmcrz7g3ADdzIelM\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"HSC Result of 2019 and last 5 Years Analytics\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1_CMBCLY9E3JRYJ2_EM9ki71CZ7CXtdYv\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"SSC Result of 2019 and last 5 Years Analytics\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/1EY2hlvCKqWAzza99cBuN2wtIGZgey5wc\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"JSC Result of 2018 and last 5 Years Analytics\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/17UOodOwr8Ia4dacTM9b8okH7LYy5XUoS\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"SSC Result - 2018 of DCGPSC\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/15S1OcVk-Sj9KMvNmdwx6RUdcM24RGtYp\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":\"fa-file-pdf\",\"open_new_tab\":false},{\"text\":\"HSC Result - 2017 of DCGPSC\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/drive.google.com\\/file\\/d\\/15FHDZJQOPG_ooILWL1CkG4ZB8c-_A-7L\\/view?usp=sharing\",\"color\":\"primary\",\"icon\":null,\"open_new_tab\":false}]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,80,'2026-04-02 00:01:41','2026-04-02 00:02:39','2026-04-02 01:31:16'),(59,'Recruitment Result','recruitment-result',NULL,'Recruitment Result',NULL,'[]',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,81,'2026-04-02 00:02:39','2026-04-02 00:03:19','2026-04-02 00:04:19'),(60,'Contact','contact',NULL,'Contact Us','<div class=\"col-sm-4\" style=\"padding-right:0px; margin-right:0px\" bis_skin_checked=\"1\">\n                <strong>Dhaka Cantt Girls\' Public School &amp; College</strong><br>Dhaka Cantonment, Bangladesh<br>\n                <strong>Office Phone No. - </strong>8711111 Ext.7720 (Civil); <br>Ext.7480 (Army)<br><br><br>\n                <strong>Helpline (8am-8pm) </strong><br>\n                <strong>Admin Related Queries- </strong> 01769017725<br>\n                <strong>Tuition Fee Related Queries – </strong> 01876862530<br><strong> Transport Related Queries – </strong> 01769051740 <br><br><br>\n                <!-- -->\n\n                <strong>College Coordinator - </strong> 01716098154 <br>\n                <strong>School Coordinator (Primary, BV) - </strong>01677003245<br>\n                <strong>School Coordinator (Secondary, BV) - </strong>01707301692<br>\n                <strong>School Coordinator (English Version)- </strong>01713190687<br>\n                <strong>E-mail  - </strong>dcgpsc2005@gmail.com\n            </div>\n\n\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3649.970486746361!2d90.3972344!3d23.8196485!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3755c6e660af53b7%3A0x1ffc06334426208c!2sDhaka%20Cantonment%20Girls&#39;%20Public%20School%20%26%20College!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sbd!4v1775112256174!5m2!1sen!2sbd\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0